{"about_the_game":"<strong>Chaos Crown</strong> is an RPG Styled Roguelite set in fantasy procedural paths. Craft artifacts, slay legendary monsters and abuse synergies to fulfill the secret goal of your champion. Which one will you choose? We need your feedback before the official launch!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509920/extras/Champions.gif?t=1733774843\" /><br><strong>CHOOSE YOUR CHAMPION</strong><br>Each champion has its own unique set of spells and skills. Which one fits your playstyle? From the mighty Toad to the sneaky Assassin, you'll probably find your favorite.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509920/extras/Combat.gif?t=1733774843\" /><br><strong>CRUSH YOUR FOES</strong><br>Clear rooms filled with monsters to progress further into the procedural path. By slaying monsters, you gain xp and sometimes basic items that you can later use to craft artifacts.<br> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509920/extras/forge7.gif?t=1733774843\" /><br><strong>CRAFT ARTIFACTS</strong><br>You can merge items together to create unique artifacts. Adapt to your loot and find creative ways to abuse synergies. This system will grow exponentially the more items are added to the game.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509920/extras/LevelUp.gif?t=1733774843\" /><br><strong>LEVEL UP</strong><br>Once you gather enough xp,  regain a portion of your health and some skill points. Spend them in a hand crafted skills tree!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509920/extras/Mazoku2.gif?t=1733774843\" /><br><strong>BARGAIN WITH THE CHAOS LORDS</strong><br>Demonic spirits will help you reach out to your goal, for a price. As you progress further, you'l